overview:
Daniel Lew has been tinkering around with computers since he was 15 years old.

From an early age Daniel left school to work in his family business Pointout Publications and to learn and develop an understanding of graphic design, it was with this he then took initiative to take this knowledge further and expand into working with printing companies, design and media companies across Australia.

Through his years of experience working in the Marketing field he then took his knowledge onto the Internet, which has developed into quite a diverse skill set, including very high levels of knowledge in the areas of search engine optimization and online marketing, along with an uncanny knack for implementing his creative ideas.

Daniel Lew was originally born on the Gold Coast in Queensland, Australia. Spending the last 6 years overseas in UK and Thailand, recently Daniel has moved back to Australia to expand his SEO business (GSEO.net) Globally with offices in Melbourne, Bangkok, London and Michigan.

His SEO and marketing skills are not the only thing that has already made and will continue to make him a valuable asset to his start up companies. His business mind and years of experience running successful web businesses, including founding Globe Search Limited, GSEO.net, developing an SEO program called Keyword Winner along with many other successful ventures has made what Daniel is today.
